Class Debris

java.lang.Object
SpaceObject
Debris
All Implemented Interfaces:
Analyzable
public class Debris extends SpaceObject implements Analyzable
The Debris class represents a space object classified as orbital debris. It extends the SpaceObject class and implements the Analyzable interface to support analysis features such as conjunctions and age.
